{"tid":2154991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大手足 ACHK 有嘢想大家幫手啊!!","createTime":"2020-08-13T12:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T15:51:06.000Z","uid":28759,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"9f64ab98625ad8bd623796131ef3754a5ccbf4e4","tid":2154991,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:44:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上個 post︰<br />\n[突發] 加拿大手足 ACHK 喺加國國會作證緊<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fNsFjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fNsFjS</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就係想大家幫手 Send Email 俾加拿大總理杜魯多<br />\n想唔想加拿大快啲跟美國制裁港官？<br />\n加拿大嘅執政黨係自由黨<br />\n對中國問題佢地一向都行得比較慢<br />\n希望大家可以一齊推佢幾下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nEmail 都幫你地 draft 好晒啦！<br />\n用緊手機嘅朋友撳呢度︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://alliancecanadahk.com/achk-email-campaign-mobile\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Falliancecanadahk.com%2Fachk-email-campaign-mobile&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=dab3ae89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://alliancecanadahk.com/achk-email-campaign-mobile</a><br />\n用緊電腦嘅朋友撳呢度︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://alliancecanadahk.com/achk-email-campaign-gmail\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Falliancecanadahk.com%2Fachk-email-campaign-gmail&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=9ec668ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://alliancecanadahk.com/achk-email-campaign-gmail</a><br />\n記住寫埋個下款先 Send <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n封信嘅大體內容同訴求︰<br />\n黎智英、周庭、李宇軒、李宗澤及最少另外六位社運人士被捕，情勢已是相當嚴峻。香港人、各個海外支援團體以及支持香港社運的加拿大人亦受威脅。<br />\n我們要求加拿大政府為港人提供「避風港」，並<strong><span class=\"red\">聯同其它國家制裁害港官員</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n原 post︰<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/alliancecanhk/posts/188941715954916\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Falliancecanhk%2Fposts%2F188941715954916&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=f9df86b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/alliancecanhk/posts/188941715954916</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">一齊塞爆杜魯多</span></span></strong>個 Email <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39564958af87a2ea995de4987ed52890c86023b","tid":2154991,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:46:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/07/07/98/8150177.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F07%2F07%2F98%2F8150177.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930&h=3ff4bfdb&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n杜魯多等緊你"},{"pid":"9fc0bdf1841666a603a08169625b90e6d83e559b","tid":2154991,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:03.000Z","msg":"ACHK 官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://alliancecanadahk.com/zh/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BCachk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Falliancecanadahk.com%2Fzh%2F%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%2596%25BCachk%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzuzNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=af97ef66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://alliancecanadahk.com/zh/%E9%97%9C%E6%96%BCachk/</a>"},{"pid":"2e03d0d9018879021f6e34a79108af90a2ae83a1","tid":2154991,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"25de72bef856420b8084075ce687ffda2030e3d6","tid":2154991,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"有冇人幫下手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2528d70f212adceb2d61951